reviews.review_content:
Rachna made froniters a survivable class. She made sure to explain each lecture VERY CLEARLY and held GREAT reviews before the midterm and the final. She was always available in her office and responded quickly to emails. If you have her for froniters consider yourself lucky!!!
Workload:
Instead of giving WIA every week she had them due after each unit (recomendation- go to the help room) and lecture questions counted more than other classes but were pretty simple- in addition there was an in class presentation that was supposed to demonstrate what you've learned in fos but was a bit annoying.
